{"tid":126042,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係唔飲得奶茶咖啡?","createTime":"2017-02-19T04:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T09:48:22.000Z","uid":69985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da42b2bc887072f06e5766061545553a9ba41250","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"我次次飲完會心跳加速，想作嘔咁<br />\n貢茶奶蓋都會咁<br />\n但天仁就無事<br />\n<br />\n會唔會關個茶底事呢?<br />\n因為飲越色果隻橙色奶茶我就無事<br />\n檸茶都無事<br />\n<br />\n已經好多年無飲過奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好懷念又香又滑既凍奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23164aa56eb87cda13bf3b0e94893b7f443908b","tid":126042,"uid":77206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"茶記呢？"},{"pid":"7437446e028dfacfbdc9cad45940befd6e8b13a0","tid":126042,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"熱奶茶同咖啡都正到仆街<br />\n唔飲得真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fc1f25938b0875941e2536ae596b7d3b9abec4","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶記呢？</blockquote><br />\n就係唔得<br />\n最鐘意茶記凍奶茶<br />\n<br />\n同埋飲完會個人變到好心急<br />\n唔知係唔係提神過頭"},{"pid":"611530afa907b1f7cab8a3ba111794a5d4f160a2","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱奶茶同咖啡都正到仆街<br />\n唔飲得真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想搵下點解，睇下有無計可以解決"},{"pid":"76b7b301dd6a75d1c4504006cc91a233544c23dd","tid":126042,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔好飲太快 要慢慢飲  唔受得咖啡因（好似係）   <br />\n我飲太濃既咖啡或者飲太快既話 飲兩啖就會頭暈心跳"},{"pid":"fbaf248ecb47a5be94c5f20c3913e6997b633ef3","tid":126042,"uid":60962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"同巴打一樣<br />\n之前我google過 <br />\n應該係受唔到咖啡因 佢當左係中毒<br />\n所以出現呢堆反應"},{"pid":"9facb197354b6f11c63410166714cfcf7cc78f40","tid":126042,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"幾年前開始一飲就全身唔舒服"},{"pid":"b154d54d61e2a696428a3e5ef55512eff32fdba9","tid":126042,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"其實你係咪對奶類敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奶茶係花奶加紅茶<br />\n咖啡都係奶加咖啡"},{"pid":"0344eda87e701f44fcdc553162aac97e454a3977","tid":126042,"uid":10879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"咁可樂得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc2a85142d29897de3048759f59788631dec577","tid":126042,"uid":35372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"咖啡除左mocha之外飲完即刻胃痛<br />\n熱奶茶唔夠熱全家都會腸胃有事<br />\n除左支裝之外出街食飯唔會飲呢兩樣"},{"pid":"9bc2e8e15a508d9559bd694437c0d178de2a117b","tid":126042,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"我飲咖啡有時都會咁<br />\n最好就唔好飲啦"},{"pid":"feffe675ad1245dfc0a8c7350770860d5ea4b7df","tid":126042,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cf9c7ce1e50d1933f73cebf074458047ac273a6","tid":126042,"uid":25855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"飲親都會胃痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384f51fab5a3e0777c0147275241792e1eac0cf0","tid":126042,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我次次飲完會心跳加速，想作嘔咁<br />\n貢茶奶蓋都會咁<br />\n但天仁就無事<br />\n<br />\n會唔會關個茶底事呢?<br />\n因為飲越色果隻橙色奶茶我就無事<br />\n檸茶都無事<br />\n<br />\n已經好多年無飲過奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好懷念又香又滑既凍奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣 飲親都出事"},{"pid":"4fef4e972941fb94c3ffac2705d2f916ef11b75f","tid":126042,"uid":72445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"我飲可樂都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係對咖啡因有反應"},{"pid":"917625b98a4879e64a8525facf01879823626ead","tid":126042,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲完咖啡會頭痛<br />\n飲完奶茶會肚瀉"},{"pid":"2d3f89f98a0c37c12324442352e830e17887cad2","tid":126042,"uid":33663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241af76cb4c1f019fd7400b64e6a507c9d7b5e6b","tid":126042,"uid":55945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:54:09.000Z","msg":"一飲咖啡就胃痛 奶茶就好少少但會滯住幾耐"},{"pid":"be946137cad29ef962b3ec214fdaf977395ced05","tid":126042,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n個人集中唔到 唔舒服<br />\n但凍飲冇事"},{"pid":"dd74d8d90f8e9c6aec251d38dfbcdd88c0d809e4","tid":126042,"uid":55945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一飲咖啡就胃痛 奶茶就好少少但會滯住<span style=\"color: red;\">幾</span>耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁"},{"pid":"6df4e98870d68accfdefa96f0a00845c20d0345d","tid":126042,"uid":60027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"應該關茶記茶底太濃事<br />\n我都係一樣唔受得茶記奶茶，心跳同胸口作悶咁<br />\n咖啡就無事"},{"pid":"aff2aff4edf27ff1394372a730d906a268d38e42","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好飲太快 要慢慢飲  唔受得咖啡因（好似係）   <br />\n我飲太濃既咖啡或者飲太快既話 飲兩啖就會頭暈心跳</blockquote><br />\n試過decaf 既咖啡都唔得<br />\n可能因為我習慣食完飯先成杯一次過飲晒<br />\n可能真係試下慢慢飲<br />\n<br />\n而家只敢放假飲，返工不了<br />\n試過有次反應勁得滯，嘔左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbf4f7aeb3e39d249f701643ad6a91e3b585708","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同巴打一樣<br />\n之前我google過 <br />\n應該係受唔到咖啡因 佢當左係中毒<br />\n所以出現呢堆反應</blockquote><br />\n試過連埋辣野一齊食，手腳會麻脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf07f0ec282f8a488b3cbc4d7848199533c544c2","tid":126042,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你係咪對奶類敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奶茶係花奶加紅茶<br />\n咖啡都係奶加咖啡</blockquote><br />\n有人話過關花奶事，但茶走一樣受唔到<br />\n<br />\n但其他奶類飲品我無問題，朝早飲奶做早餐"}]}